s within the holy sites by aligning them with infrastructure projects and supporting services, including water and energy networks and safety systems. This enhances site readiness and ensures the sustainability of operational performance during peak periods. The project to replace and upgrade the fire and cooling networks within the tent enclosures in Mina has been completed. The project encompassed the development of 188 residential areas comprising 565 camps, with a total network length of 339,000 linear meters. This was implemented in four development phases to ensure continuity of work. The first two phases included the development of 121 enclosures and 433 camps, covering an area of 275,000 linear meters. The third phase included the development of 22 enclosures and 53 camps, covering an area of 31,000 linear meters. The fourth phase covered 45 enclosures and 79 camps, covering an area of 32,000 linear meters.", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["king abdulaziz road", "al-khaif mosque", "mina", "pilgrim tents"], "creator": ["saudi gazette report"], "language": "english", "country": ["saudi arabia"], "category": ["tourism", "top"], "datatype": "news", "pubDate": "2026-05-11 16:00:35", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-05-11 16:13:37", "image_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa/saudigazette/uploads/images/2026/05/11/2706272.webp", "video_url": null, "source_id": "saudigazette", "source_name": "Saudi Gazette", "source_priority": 356263, "source_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/saudigazette.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "sentiment_stats": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_tag": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_region": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_org": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_summary": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "duplicate": false}, {"article_id": "89f42027d5947ca893c29a545c