8\u0627\u0644\u0628\u062d\u0631\u064a\u0629) \u0628\u0627\u0654\u062d\u062f\u062b \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0654\u062c\u0647\u0632\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0642\u0646\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u064a \u064a\u0639\u0645\u0644 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0647\u0627 \u0643\u0648\u0627\u062f\u0631 \u0628\u0634\u0631\u064a\u0629 \u0645\u0648\u0654\u0647\u0644\u0629 \u0628\u0644\u063a\u0627\u062a \u0636\u064a\u0648\u0641 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u062d\u0645\u0646.", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": null, "creator": null, "language": "arabic", "country": ["saudi arabia"], "category": ["lifestyle", "top"], "datatype": "news", "pubDate": "2026-05-11 16:00:00", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-05-11 16:17:37", "image_url": null, "video_url": null, "source_id": "alyaum", "source_name": "Alyaum", "source_priority": 933841, "source_url": "https://www.alyaum.com", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/alyaum.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "sentiment_stats": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_tag": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_region": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_org": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_summary": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "duplicate": false}, {"article_id": "5539df07f2a891a01f5426c3916f5967", "link": "https://www.alyaum.com/articles/6661329/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%85%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%85/%D8%AE%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%84-48-%D8%B3%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A9-%D8%A5%D9%86%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%B0-%D8%AD%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%A9-4-%D8%AD%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%AC-%D8%B9%D8%A8%D8%B1-%D8%AA%D8%AF%D8%AE%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%AC%D9%84%D8%A9-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D9%85%D9%83%D8%A9", "title": "\u062e\u0644\u0627\u0644 48 \u0633\u0627\u0639\u0629.. \u0627\u0655\u0646\u0642\u0627\u0630 \u062d\u064a\u0627\u0629 4 \u062d\u062c\u0627\u062c \u0639\u0628\u0631 \u062a\u062f\u062e\u0644\u0627\u062a \u0642\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0629 \u0639\u0627\u062c\u0644\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u0645\u0643\u0629", "description": "\u0646\u062c\u062d \u0645\u0631\u0643\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0644\u0628 \u0628<a href=\"https://www.alyaum.com/articles/6660031/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%85%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%85/%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%A9-%D8%B3%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%B9%D8%A9-%D8%B7%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D9%85%D9%83%D8%A9-%D8%AA%D9%86%D9%82%D8%B0-%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%AC%D8%A7-%D9%87%D9%86%D8%AF%D9%8A%D8%A7-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%AC%D9%84%D8%B7%D8%A9-%D9%82%D9%84%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%A9\" target=\"_blank\">\u0645\u062f\u064a\u0646\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643 \u0639\u0628\u062f\u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0628\u064a\u0629</a>\u060c \u0639\u0636\u0648 <a href=\"https://www.alyaum.com/articles/6661262/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%85%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%85/%D9%85%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B4%D9%81%D9%89-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D9%88%D8%B1-%D9%8A%D9%86%D8%AC%D8%AD-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%A6%D8%B5%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%81%D8%B5-%D8%B1%D8%A6%D9%88%D9%8A-%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%B6%D8%A9-%D8%B9%D8%A8%D8%B1-%D9%81%D8%AA%D8%AD%D8%A9-%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%AD%D8%AF%D8%A9-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%B8%D8%A7%D8%B1\" target=\"_blank\">\u062a\u062c\u0645\u0639 \u0645\u0643\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0643\u0631\u0645\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u062d\u064a</a>\u060c \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0655\u0646\u0642\u0627\u0630 \u062d\u064a\u0627\u0629 \u0627\u0654\u0631\u0628\u0639\u0629 \u0645\u0646 <a href=\"https://www.alyaum.com/articles/6661266/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%85%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%85/%D8%A8%D9%85%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%B9%D8%A9-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%A3%D9%85%D9%8A%D8%B1-%D8%AA%D8%A8%D9%88%D9%83-%D9%88%D8%AE%D8%AF%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%85%D8%AA%D9%83%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84%D8%A9-%D9%85